snippet.textDisplay:
Hello Jarvis,
I hope that you don't mind me sharing this here, but you'll find it interesting.
No B.S.
I am the Motivating Voice of Influence that Lit the Fire to The Original Infinity Ward Developer's that caused them to reunite for the Current Modern Warfare Series!
The Reintroduction of Captain Price is also due to my credit. In the First Campaign Mission when he Snipes the Bad Guy Right Before he can shoot into the oncoming vehicle, then all of a sudden a Sniper Shot takes his dome off, and the Camera zooms out to Find Captain Price "ON TOP OF A BUILDING" as the location from where he fired the shot, is all my idea!
The Idea to Reboot the Series comes from me as I Expressed & Explained using the Matrix as an example as to how we could do away with the last 6-7 years of COD which have Sucked.. IMO by pretending that they never really existed in reality! Hence "BRINGING BACK DEAD CHARACTERS"
I also Expressed & Explained as to how we could fight for a EMP to destroy all of the New Style Electronic Gameplay! Hence "GOING DARK" In the Teaser Trailer.
Its all in my Video
Titled : Call of Duty Black Ops4 Rant
By: Mr.CleanSS
Published : May 18 2018
As a 46 yr young Gamer I missed the Good Ole Days of COD and that is what inspired me to record the Video.
I do apologize in advance for the Harsh Language, it was all out of Passion for my Favorite Game!
My Interllectual Concepts & Imagination led Infinity Ward to the Lake & to the Bank.
I'm currently waiting on my Physical Copyright to return.
When it does and I get this Behind me I would love to find as many of my M&G Clan members and Challenge you Young Men @ Faze! Who knows we can possibly make it a Reality Show. We're all of 40 so you guys should definitely have a reflex advantage lol
Thank you'll and I hope y'all enjoying Modern Warfare!!
